{"id":"9f3b52f9-faad-45f9-8957-608d7cd049a5","name":"𝐁𝐫𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐬 ’𝐁𝐥𝐮𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐤’ 𝐖𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐰𝐨𝐨𝐝","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"gif\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/wu6vz4.gif\">𝐁𝐫𝐮𝐭𝐮𝐬 ’𝐁𝐥𝐮𝐞𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐤’ 𝐖𝐞𝐬𝐭𝐰𝐨𝐨𝐝</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">“<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/7hN5TKSdRb56uytwIpcUES?si=67hNGVXuT9GA0R3hS6-Ypw\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">𝒾𝒻 𝓎𝑜𝓊'𝓇𝑒 𝒽𝒶𝓋𝒾𝓃' 𝑔𝒾𝓇𝓁 𝓅𝓇𝑜𝒷𝓁𝑒𝓂𝓈 𝒾 𝒻𝑒𝑒𝓁 𝒷𝒶𝒹 𝒻𝑜𝓇 𝓎𝑜𝓊 𝓈𝑜𝓃, 𝒾 𝑔𝑜𝓉 𝟿𝟿 𝓅𝓇𝑜𝒷𝓁𝑒𝓂𝓈 𝒷𝓊𝓉 𝒶 𝒷𝒾𝓉𝒸𝒽 𝒶𝒾𝓃'𝓉 𝑜𝓃𝑒</a>,”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">~~꧂ <em>𝟗𝟗 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐛𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐬 ✰ 𝐡𝐮𝐠𝐨</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_4b5674cb-061e-43de-8944-3f0a4c52176c.webp?width=1000\">𝐏𝐑𝐄𝐒𝐈𝐃𝐄𝐍𝐓 𝐁𝐋𝐔𝐄𝐓𝐈𝐂𝐊</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">~~꧂ The one where the prez of Appalachia’s largest MC is headed to Detroit for the Savage Nomad Throttlefest. Backseat empty and ready to get rowdy with the boys, Bluetick finds himself puttin’ his money where his mouth is at a dive diner on the way there. Daring a hot little thing waiting tables to up and leave with him? To the craziest party this side a’ Rockies?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You’re in for a wild ride, honeylamb.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_6f7edead-3757-4a4a-a50f-428d69aba5c4.webp?width=1000\">𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐇𝐎𝐋𝐋𝐄𝐑 𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐍𝐃𝐒 𝐌𝐂</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_0c1d87e7-dc7d-49aa-8fab-2a32a1685a57.webp?width=1000\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_c525f316-5651-41d0-bddc-5ea495ce4e40.webp?width=1000\">~~ <em>𝐓𝐰 &amp; 𝐜𝐰</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>𝐌𝐚𝐧’𝐬 𝐠𝐨𝐭 𝐚 𝐥𝐢𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐤𝐬, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐢𝐬 𝐦𝐞𝐚𝐧 𝐧𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐲 𝐛𝐮𝐭 𝐢𝐧 𝐚 ’𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐫𝐲𝐨𝐧𝐞 𝐛𝐮𝐭 𝐲𝐨𝐮’ 𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐝𝐚 𝐰𝐚𝐲. 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐦𝐮𝐫𝐝𝐞𝐫 𝐢𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐛𝐚𝐜𝐤𝐬𝐭𝐨𝐫𝐲, 𝐝𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝐢𝐧 𝐝𝐫𝐮𝐠𝐬, 𝐢𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐥 𝐚𝐥𝐜𝐨𝐡𝐨𝐥, 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐰𝐞𝐚𝐩𝐨𝐧𝐬! 𝐇𝐨𝐩𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐠𝐮𝐲𝐬 𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐟𝐮𝐧, <s><mark style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: inherit\">𝐑𝐄𝐀𝐃 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐌𝐅𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐊𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒 𝐁𝐄𝐅𝐎𝐑𝐄 𝐃𝐈𝐕𝐈𝐍𝐆 𝐈𝐍</mark></s>, 𝐡𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐲𝐛𝐮𝐧𝐬 ❤️</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>~~ 𝐌𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐬</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>𝐀𝐩𝐚𝐫𝐭 𝐨𝐟 @</em><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/74f15eed-812b-49f7-944e-b4d5ef34bad4_profile-of-leidenpotato\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>𝐥𝐞𝐢𝐝𝐞𝐧𝐩𝐨𝐭𝐚𝐭𝐨</em></a><em> 𝐬𝐚𝐯𝐚𝐠𝐞 𝐧𝐨𝐦𝐚𝐝 𝐜𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐚𝐛!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>𝐀𝐧𝐝 @</em><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/98cb8e25-664f-4c84-81b3-5441ee9bb386_profile-of-keedacat-2026/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><em>𝐩𝐥𝐮𝐦𝐩𝐫𝐮𝐦𝐩</em></a><em> 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐞𝐫 𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐬 𝐩𝐚𝐭𝐜𝐡!</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/251e61dc-5339-4372-863f-9adfec3c5e5b_f438f985-21f5-4063-9749-37ad76723105.webp?width=1000\">𝐖𝐀𝐍𝐍𝐀 𝐌𝐄𝐄𝐓 𝐓𝐇𝐄 𝐇𝐎𝐋𝐋𝐄𝐑 𝐇𝐎𝐔𝐍𝐃 𝐑𝐈𝐕𝐀𝐋𝐒 𝐀𝐍𝐃 𝐀𝐋𝐋𝐈𝐄𝐒?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Find both over with @<a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/ec692a95-d044-4680-a745-f3acaba3f9fe_profile-of-caithart?mode=all&amp;sort=popular&amp;search=Caithart&amp;page=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">caithart</a>, <s>mean nasty</s> <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7007251e-6f38-471d-88c6-6f362e94cdb4_character-fergus-butcher-mac-leod-blood-kings-mc\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Blood Kings</a>, and the Road Wraithes and the loml <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/19198d43-4ea5-45a9-9ca1-10d101671cfd_character-vernon-duke-